____________________ Django-Class Based View ____________________

    - Takes a request and returns a response
    - More than just a function
    - Example of some classes which can be used as views
    - Allow - structure your views and reuse code
    - Alternative way to implement views
    - Organization of code related to specific HTTP methods (GET, POST, etc.)
    - HttpRequest and expected back an HttpResponse.


